{"tid":1881454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[證據] ig所有新account賣口罩 要你like share comment 全部都係假","createTime":"2020-02-15T14:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T04:33:40.000Z","uid":37559,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f95d56ab502db9f630eddd844182ed4358480591","tid":1881454,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實有好多巴絲開過post講呢樣野，但係我直至今日仲見到d朋友post呢d story，所以想開多個post講<br />\n<br />\n總之就係要你like+share佢地張相去story，跟住再comment要幾盒thanks! 要tag埋唔知幾多個朋友，最危險就係可能<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要你填google form攞你個人資料</span></span><br />\n佢地呃人個原理同新年嗰一排要你like share comment tag幾個人嗰d抽獎一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的：</span></span><br />\n1. 短時間内免費呃大量follower，跟住轉用途<br />\n2. 攞個人資料<br />\ne.g. 名、電話、居住區、話俾學生既口罩可能要講學校、話俾香港人既口罩可能要身份證號碼......<br />\n3. 要你comment 光復香港，時代革命 / 黑警死全家... 確認身份，以後清算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證據：</span></span><br />\n我之前揾口罩揾到好desperate，見到朋友story share非炒價賣口罩俾真香港人，我又share埋一份，仲填左份google form，講左ig名、電話、想要幾多盒口罩<br />\n(achieve裏面揾唔返個story，但係當時有個朋友reply過我)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCM7kdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCM7kdk.png&h=29f14d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時我睇已經有三萬幾人留左言，估計佢已經得到最少幾萬人既ig名同埋電話<br />\n最後個account緊係話 &ldquo;太多人要，名額已滿...&rdquo; 最後就無咗件事<br />\n<br />\n今日我個story突然彈左個奇怪account @dd_photoss (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dd_photoss/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdd_photoss%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=dc61941d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/dd_photoss/</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDttO6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDttO6g.jpg&h=c2c5fe14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我以爲係廣告，望真d原來係我follow既人嚟，但係我好肯定我無亦都唔會follow過呢個人<br />\n睇返我following list，個影相account係我最近follow既，我最近新follow既account唔多，唯一就係個口罩account無左 (我無unfollow佢)，<br />\n而且當時有一齊share口罩story既人，都不約而同follow左影相account<br />\ntldr: 賣口罩既ig呃完follower，就轉做影相account @dd_photoss<br />\n<br />\n其實唔夠買唔到口罩都唔緊要，咪出少d街囉，但係個人資料俾左出去就無得收返<br />\n大家可以笑我地on9，但係今日既香港大部分人都需要口罩，我地都係想多個辦法買到口罩，有貨先比錢聽落又無損失，所以先會中伏<br />\n邊諗到會有人利用香港人既焦急去呃人呢咁無恥？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家同你既朋友講，絕對唔好信賣/送口罩既新account！</span></span><br />\n最後祝大家身體健康！<br />\n一齊欣賞下@dd_photoss 影既靚相啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5Y5Rup.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5Y5Rup.png&h=f46e2474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZfG9f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZfG9f5.png&h=933d2be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oeJtPf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeJtPf5.png&h=2e59b3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Orjbur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Orjbur.png&h=033f6dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4es4Pr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4es4Pr.png&h=cd930008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esYxwus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesYxwus.png&h=4e2e10eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFTfV8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFTfV8.png&h=5cd75b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2hXBX9t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2hXBX9t.png&h=8273966f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GXKnA9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GXKnA9.png&h=2309a83f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c950f8826f43e1fa0039e